A major concept in machine learning is neural networks. In neural networks, there are many layers in the network and each layer is connected to every layer. The network learns from the past data. Neural networks can be used to solve machine learning algorithms like linear algebra which is very complex. However, neural networks take a lot of time to compute. As a result, a deep learning neural network is used which is much more efficient and can result in better performance.

If we look at the definition of the concept in the picture on left, we can have a quick understanding of deep learning. It says that there are several hidden layers between the input layer and the output layer which improves the accuracy of the model. However, this is not the full concept.

To understand deep learning, let's take a look at an example on right.

